notes on irrigation module development

# overall structure

what is the best way of linking the various modules - some of which
may be supplied from extenal models?

-> NetCDF? i.e. coupling through i/o (loose model coupling)

in this case, since the demand module is going to be coupled with
different models, we should develop a simple hydrological model
alongside the water demand model, but keep it as a separate model
which writes output at each time step.

data exchange:

vegetation parameters
groundwater level
soil water content
rooting depth

it should be possible for *all* model variables to be written to
file. User should specify which variables should be written to file
and also provide a filename template. 
